column5: was it cold out cause I see you're turteling... the one black pup with the white tuff looks very much like my old girl.

Thats slicks, shes 5 now. Very good girl! Im a little peeved at her as she decided to kill 2 skunks the other night and it wreaks to high hell in the yard right now.  The other was our boxer. Awesome dog! She passed 4 years ago after being poisoned with anti freeze. Never found out who did it though, and that might be a good thing because id probably be in a cell right now
